strings: <voice_0x010014CD><se_low>*: It does not change day or night. But I still feel as if I am back in time.
<voice_0x010014CF><se_low>*: Come once daily. I always believed that someday it would take me closer to heaven...
Those who could do it had no choice but to watch the slow passage of time. And they're stuck in the lake of Purgatory...
